        "description": "Listing of communication with candidates for a specific position.\n\n#### Requirements\n\n* The call must include an authorization token.\n* New token type:\n    * The token must have the `api.position.write` permission.\n* Old token types:\n    * Token type: `public_access`, `full_access`\n",
