    "/enums/channels": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Enumerations"
        ],
        "summary": "Get Company channels",
        "description": "Retrieves all publication channels on which the given company can publish job advertisements. \nWhen filtering job ads, the channel ID can then be used as an argument.\n\n#### Requirements\n\n* The call must include an authorization token.\n* Compatible with the company token.\n* New token type:\n    * The token must have the `api.enums.read` permission.\n* Old token types:\n    * Token type: `public_access`, `full_access`\n",
