        "description": "Returns all sources and their IDs. Sources can be defined either by the system itself \nor added manually by the company.\n\n#### Requirements\n\n* The call must include an authorization token.\n* Compatible with the company token.\n* New token type:\n    * The token must have the `api.enums.read` permission.\n* Old token types:\n    * Token type: `public_access`, `full_access`\n",
