      "post": {
        "summary": "Domain verification",
        "description": "This webhook is called when attempting to save a webhook in the application UI settings.  \nTo complete the verification successfully, proceed as follows:\n- Take the code that this webhook sends you in `body.verification`\n- Send this code back in the body (send only the code itself, without the keyword \u201cverification\u201d)\n\nThe content of the header is not relevant for validation.\n",
